      "id": "257174b8-2802-4277-92ba-5a2d1a78aee3",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Question 3: \n\nWrite a program to assign 9 students into 3 groups randomly\n\nHere is the code to randomize an integer\nimport java.util.Random;\n…\n        Random rand = new Random();\n        int temp = rand.nextInt();\n",
