      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "//String is immutable --> create same content at same address\r\nString s1 =\"hehe\";\r\nString s2 = s1;\r\nString s3 = \"hehe\";\r\nIO.println(s1==s2);\r\nIO.println(s2==s3);\r\nIO.println(s1==s3);",
